<paragraph id="A6C7CFF954AC6FDAAD21AB4967C55575" pageId="null" pageNumber="44">
<taxonomicName id="FCCC894FCDB5A6EEAC45EF558FBC87A6" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Convolvulaceae" genus="Convolvulus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Solanales" pageId="null" pageNumber="44" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">Convolvulus</taxonomicName>
<normalizedToken id="712DEAB7CDBDBCF947B54A7A58F6FC38" originalValue="cantábricus" pageId="null" pageNumber="44">cantabricus</normalizedToken>
<authorityName id="7F3C021F690ED5157DBB1B98D5588F56" pageId="null" pageNumber="44">L.</authorityName>
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="83CDF1A303A2FCB524F145E795BEF12B" pageId="null" pageNumber="44" type="vernacular_names">
<paragraph id="260AA898BCE4B84C1E8CF90B06A6E661" pageId="null" pageNumber="44">Kantabrische Winde</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
</title>
<subSubSection id="DA6D1104D09E83B0D2EADEC8468B002F" pageId="null" pageNumber="44" type="description">
<paragraph id="9604DD62A84D19E5074676416AB7E8CB" pageId="null" pageNumber="44">
Ausdauernd, 20-40 cm hoch, 
<emphasis id="A365FCD8C5555C5C6A7EA31928A56951" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="44">meist aufrecht</emphasis>
, selten niederliegend, 
<emphasis id="8E059E3C81D2FDB22E4B3CE9C35C1E67" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="44">nie windend; ganze Pflanze ziemlich dicht, lang und braun behaart</emphasis>
, mit mehreren Stengeln. 
<emphasis id="43D4948FE2F8A884A16EB9D4ED496942" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="44">
<normalizedToken id="E047E1CA5D4736F3069CE53B08858ACA" originalValue="Blätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="44">Blaetter</normalizedToken>
schmal oval oder schmal lanzettlich
</emphasis>
, bis 8 cm lang, 6-10mal so lang wie breit, ganzrandig oder entfernt 
<normalizedToken id="0F4627287804B3D6D32EF1CED094FF05" originalValue="gezähnt" pageId="null" pageNumber="44">gezaehnt</normalizedToken>
, die untersten 
<normalizedToken id="999CBC42B2B34AC417E71C8501F91F02" originalValue="allmählich" pageId="null" pageNumber="44">allmaehlich</normalizedToken>
in einen kurzen Stiel 
<normalizedToken id="77D238B1EC940072155D84380545C7EC" originalValue="verschmälert" pageId="null" pageNumber="44">verschmaelert</normalizedToken>
, die obern sitzend. 
<normalizedToken id="BBAD4E00D34D090CE4BCCFE2FC63460E" originalValue="Blütenstiele" pageId="null" pageNumber="44">Bluetenstiele</normalizedToken>
in Blattachseln und 
<normalizedToken id="BBA7EA2C8B4DD680AD04BBC9D2550AD3" originalValue="endständig" pageId="null" pageNumber="44">endstaendig</normalizedToken>
, 1-5 
<normalizedToken id="2F1CBCFAD99184F313FEAC1216ACC523" originalValue="blütig" pageId="null" pageNumber="44">bluetig</normalizedToken>
, mindestens die untern bis 10mal so lang wie die 
<normalizedToken id="550D64D993D71FC47975F1837F584BA0" originalValue="Blüten" pageId="null" pageNumber="44">Blueten</normalizedToken>
. 
<normalizedToken id="D2A4BA22016455DE12828372E4B168A6" originalValue="Vorblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="44">Vorblaetter</normalizedToken>
2, 
<emphasis id="B1E3E9E423ED983E29EC90256CC20009" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="44">
schmal lanzettlich bis 
<normalizedToken id="CC2B539C954C49EAA1EB6B23644B36FA" originalValue="fadenförmig" pageId="null" pageNumber="44">fadenfoermig</normalizedToken>
, wenig unterhalb des Kelches angewachsen, 
<normalizedToken id="F7846773C4029CC552DF0F3CF4F43E9A" originalValue="länger" pageId="null" pageNumber="44">laenger</normalizedToken>
als die 
<normalizedToken id="80C714EBDDC2F2EF09B0A04781A72206" originalValue="Kelchblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="44">Kelchblaetter</normalizedToken>
</emphasis>
. 
<normalizedToken id="D829B41EA47720AEB80016D7F31E8104" originalValue="Kelchblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="44">Kelchblaetter</normalizedToken>
5-8 mm lang, 
<normalizedToken id="D8B5B5EEBF8EB705DF59866DA7F77086" originalValue="plötzlich" pageId="null" pageNumber="44">ploetzlich</normalizedToken>
in die Spitze 
<normalizedToken id="BEBCD1C5D86993735FF93CE50CFED2AE" originalValue="verschmälert" pageId="null" pageNumber="44">verschmaelert</normalizedToken>
. Krone weit 
<normalizedToken id="B44AD9D2F6454D8C9AF7501E1B72581A" originalValue="trichterförmig" pageId="null" pageNumber="44">trichterfoermig</normalizedToken>
, 
<emphasis id="D621D8D21B0EBF5B46D50D2E1C6A0487" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="44">rosa</emphasis>
, 1,5-2,5 cm lang, 
<emphasis id="B6D29EE017CAD1BD6CC4228A19AF8124" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="44">
<normalizedToken id="B0ED6CD5ECABEA2FC4224CFB55ADBF21" originalValue="außerseits" pageId="null" pageNumber="44">ausserseits</normalizedToken>
mit 5 behaarten Streifen
</emphasis>
(im Gebiet nur bei dieser Art so!). 
<normalizedToken id="CC65002DCDF1D3B90902C55CFD4B6D58" originalValue="Staubfäden" pageId="null" pageNumber="44">Staubfaeden</normalizedToken>
ohne 
<normalizedToken id="969ADB8A141DC0EBF9C5AB5807C48C0C" originalValue="Drüsenhaare" pageId="null" pageNumber="44">Druesenhaare</normalizedToken>
. Griffel mit 2 
<normalizedToken id="0FB24A35F33111205F082FB7E1EBFA25" originalValue="fadenförmigen" pageId="null" pageNumber="44">fadenfoermigen</normalizedToken>
Narben. Fruchtkapsel kugelig, Durchmesser 5-8 mm. - 
<normalizedToken id="BB274746D1F2D774E0814EFD135E2F76" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="44">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: Sommer.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="F4BB23527F68BE287082834C859077D0" pageId="null" pageNumber="44">
<emphasis id="E6327DBF5218C557C737F2E175C1EB11" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="44">Zytologische Angaben. 2n</emphasis>
= 
<emphasis id="DD87E92071B3883EBDEB469D643A0E60" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="44">22:</emphasis>
Material aus Italien (Dolcher und Pignatti 1960). 
<emphasis id="4E805C402926288459D282678472833E" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="44">2n</emphasis>
= 
<emphasis id="7DC763BB2461BB26FD34EF604AE56942" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="44">30:</emphasis>
Material aus Ungarn (Baksay 1958).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="AEFFE23EEA2E171684ED6637B6C31F74" pageId="null" pageNumber="44">
<emphasis id="B26F0FE8B7F031A00FA50E0BDED6E2BF" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="44">Standort</emphasis>
. Kollin. Trockene, sandige bis lehmige 
<normalizedToken id="DA39534F222CC91ACB2DF2B71A255EF2" originalValue="Böden" pageId="null" pageNumber="44">Boeden</normalizedToken>
in 
<normalizedToken id="B24381248227FA916BEDAB78D643A82A" originalValue="heißen" pageId="null" pageNumber="44">heissen</normalizedToken>
Lagen. 
<normalizedToken id="513B098946078358E14AA92BCE593AB8" originalValue="Äcker" pageId="null" pageNumber="44">Aecker</normalizedToken>
, felsige 
<normalizedToken id="BC5C9C8AAE3BDBB5716BA9BDDF448FD8" originalValue="Hänge" pageId="null" pageNumber="44">Haenge</normalizedToken>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="A2EFD944601F0C22A5D23C73266C8DBC" pageId="null" pageNumber="44">
<emphasis id="A997ADB27B111AC859A5391E721E99D9" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="44">Verbreitung. Mediterrane Pflanze:</emphasis>
Ganzes Mediterrangebiet, 
<normalizedToken id="98ED273A8A7D332DC99C8A754B925C65" originalValue="nordwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="44">nordwaerts</normalizedToken>
bis 
<normalizedToken id="0602965BC48E3646BCF9B2200BE85479" originalValue="Puy-de-Dôme" pageId="null" pageNumber="44">Puy-de-Dome</normalizedToken>
, 
<normalizedToken id="76BE121882883563BDF2FB247ECA344F" originalValue="Dép" pageId="null" pageNumber="44">Dep</normalizedToken>
. Ain, 
<normalizedToken id="973B9A11C4FC769CDF7E65CC8E769D81" originalValue="Alpensüdfuß" pageId="null" pageNumber="44">Alpensuedfuss</normalizedToken>
, Wiener Becken; 
<normalizedToken id="D0935063E35705C0BD6BF632565C3D4E" originalValue="ostwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="44">ostwaerts</normalizedToken>
bis Krim und Kaukasus. - Im Gebiet: 
<normalizedToken id="74BD86A83B8580EA3B1C350CC2A4793E" originalValue="Dép" pageId="null" pageNumber="44">Dep</normalizedToken>
. Ain (
<normalizedToken id="BE70A3CFD398C436047B605D942DD4B6" originalValue="südlicher" pageId="null" pageNumber="44">suedlicher</normalizedToken>
Teil), Bergamasker Alpen (zwischen Predore und Sarnico am Lago 
<normalizedToken id="172A3A9B64C25444FBD3002D39F3F84B" originalValue="d’Iseo" pageId="null" pageNumber="44">d'Iseo</normalizedToken>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
